Group Executive Committee





Al-Noor Ramji
Group Chief Digital Officer
Al-Noor, who joined Prudential in January 2016 in the newly created role of Group Chief Digital Officer, is responsible for developing and executing an integrated, long-term digital strategy for the Group. 
Before joining Prudential, he worked at Northgate Capital, a venture capital firm in Silicon Valley, where he ran the technology-focused funds. 
Prior to this Al-Noor was at Misys, the financial services software group, and he has previously held leading technology and innovation roles at BT Group, Qwest Communications, Dresdner Kleinwort Benson and Swiss Bank Corporation.

