Al-Noor Ramji is Chief Strategy Officer of Calypso and one of the leading information technology (IT) experts in the telecommunications and financial industries. Prior to Calypso, he was the executive vice president and general manager of Misys Banking. Previously, he served in various executive roles at British Telecom, including chief executive officer for BT Innovate and Design and chief information officer and chief technology officer of BT Group. Prior to British Telecom, he was executive vice president, chief information officer and chief e-commerce officer for Qwest Communications. Mr. Ramji has also served as chief information officer at UBS (then called SBC) and, prior to UBS, as global head of operations at Credit Suisse First Boston.



